00:02.866 --> 00:22.473
for what I did not have. During your student era, 
Describe generally the attitudes of the typical

00:28.111 --> 00:34.037
Aggie student. Were they rich, poor, 
conservative, liberal, what? Conservative and

00:39.643 --> 00:41.465
poor. There were a handful of guys that had cars, so 
you thought they were rich. Just to have a car, you

00:47.852 --> 00:49.694
had to be rich. And where did they come from 
geographically? Everywhere. And in today's

00:55.668 --> 01:02.441
politically correct definition of diversity, 
how diverse was the student body? It wasn't. It

01:04.165 --> 01:04.646
wasn't. I remember quite a few Hispanics, like I 
described earlier. I know drill team. We had an

01:11.079 --> 01:16.309
enormous number of guys from Central Catholic 
High School. And how were those Hispanics

01:16.593 --> 01:18.495
treated? Just like, I think everybody was treated 
just exactly the same. I don't think there was a bit

01:22.558 --> 01:24.000
of difference. To my knowledge, there was no 
difference while I was a student. Were there any,

01:29.765 --> 01:36.671
well, by the time you graduated, there were some 
black students. There were a handful. I didn't

01:38.072 --> 01:39.413
personally know any. I knew them, you know, just I 
knew some names of two or three of them, but I didn't

01:39.674 --> 01:45.739
really know any of them. All right. How does that 
relate to whatever Aggie spirit is? What is Aggie

01:52.631 --> 01:53.992
spirit?

02:01.300 --> 02:16.637
The impact is that I think you end up with knowing 
individuals, be they student friends that become

02:01.300 --> 02:16.637
lifelong members or the even if it is two or three 
faculty or staff that you remember, the impact of

02:17.174 --> 02:39.780
silver taps and muster and a few ceremonies, and 
the fact that you had an experience that just molds

02:17.174 --> 02:39.780
you to be prepared to do whatever you decide you 
want to do. And that ends up equaling a spirit. And

02:45.322 --> 02:53.354
then you learn right away that the former students 
that are out there are going to accept you

02:45.322 --> 02:53.354
immediately.

