couldn't afford to go that summer or I would have 
probably gone. It would have been good for me if I

05:18.876 --> 05:20.678
could have gone. Because I today think that part of 
the Aggie spirit. We have 4,000 freshmen of 6,300

05:25.003 --> 05:28.848
that go through fish camp. And so they get 
connected immediately. Yep, yep. You have 11,000

05:32.080 --> 05:37.727
kids live on campus out of the 36,000 
undergraduates. It's huge. The residential

05:39.337 --> 05:47.489
living is a huge part of feeling connected and 
knowing people and the involvement level. And

05:48.150 --> 05:53.738
I'll bring back another day for just a five or ten 
minute visit. I've got some data gathered. If you

05:58.285 --> 06:07.318
measure the quality of the student body by the 
percentage of all undergraduates who were in the

05:58.285 --> 06:07.318
top ten percent of their high school class, This is 
