08:16.460 --> 08:22.450
learn now in its broadest? I think that I had 
reinforced family values of integrity. I think I

08:30.383 --> 08:32.106
learned integrity. I learned common sense, hard 
work, the right way to do something. began to learn

08:40.203 --> 08:51.301
the importance of friendships and how to nurture 
them and make them work and appreciate them.

08:55.087 --> 09:02.920
